column2: SELECT p.ra, p.dec, p.g, p.r, s.z, s.snMedian_r, s.velDisp, s.velDisperr, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.chunk, s.boss_target1, stM.logMass, p.fiber2Mag_u, p.fiber2MagErr_u, p.fiber2Mag_g, p.fiber2MagErr_g, p.fiber2Mag_r, p.fiber2MagErr_r, p.fiber2Mag_i, p.fiber2MagErr_i, p.fiber2Mag_z, p.fiber2MagErr_z, p.extinction_u, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_i, p.extinction_z, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMagErr_i, stM.age, stMS.SFR FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN stellarMassPassivePort AS stM ON s.specObjID = stM.specObjID JOIN stellarMassStarformingPort as stMS ON s.specObjID = stMS.specObjID WHERE s.z BETWEEN # AND # AND s.survey = # AND s.class = # AND s.snMedian_r > = # AND s.velDIsp BETWEEN # AND # AND s.zWARNING = #
